blogs.title: React
blogs.author: Facebook
blogs.body: React is a popular JavaScript library for building fast and interactive user interfaces. Developed by Facebook, it has become one of the most widely used tools for web development.

blogs.title: Vue
blogs.author: Evan You
blogs.body: Vue.js is a progressive JavaScript framework for building user interfaces. Created by Evan You, Vue is known for its simplicity and flexibility, making it a popular choice for developers.

blogs.title: Angular
blogs.author: Google
blogs.body: Angular is a full-featured JavaScript framework developed by Google. It provides a robust solution for building complex, scalable web applications, supporting both desktop and mobile platforms.
